name: box3
description: Woah! Third box and moving on, great job! Okay, you know it ... you will need to initialize your project again from scratch. C'mon stop complaining! Life is not easy, you know that! It's time to struggle in some algorithm... what about implementing a sort algorithm? I don't care about which will you do... just make it happens! Kind advise: DON'T USE A BUILTIN FUNCTION, this will take you out of the competition.
